86
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:17,740
How can you let your own child have the same suffering?

87
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:19,000
She's just a daughter.

88
00:05:19,670 --> 00:05:23,070
The previous two daughters of the concubines were treated the same way.

89
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:24,130
It doesn't matter.

90
00:05:25,180 --> 00:05:26,040
What matters is

91
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:30,050
to give birth to a grandson for Father to make him happy.

92
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:34,670
Go find more chaste girls

93
00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:36,680
and bring them in secretly.

94
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,100
Don't tell anyone.

95
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:40,920
Your Highness!

96
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:43,760
You want to get new concubines at this time?

97
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,760
I have the final say in this mansion.

98
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,990
You just need to do as I say.

99
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,600
It's fine that you want new concubines.

100
00:05:55,180 --> 00:05:56,010
But please

101
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,680
