107
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,880
and get married with respectable identity.

108
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,740
The eldest legitimate daughter?

109
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:19,190
Stop dreaming.

110
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:23,010
