114
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,130
Nothing.

115
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:37,180
You may leave.

116
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,060
Your Ladyship, you're grounded. Please reflect on yourself here.

117
00:07:15,060 --> 00:07:16,920
Don't go out without permission.

118
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:05,700
Your Ladyship.

119
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:07,920
I found it.

120
00:08:17,350 --> 00:08:21,210
I never expected that the reason why I couldn't give birth for so many years

121
00:08:21,210 --> 00:08:22,540
could be...

122
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:33,110
Sorceress Zhang came today

123
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:36,570
and gave these to the people serving Prince Song.

124
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:40,220
Rapeseed, radix rehmanniae, angelica and Ligusticum wallichii [Chinese herbal medicinal ingredients].

125
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,809
It's hard to notice

126
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:44,530
what these ingredients are for/make up.

127
00:08:46,590 --> 00:08:48,720
I've been watching over in the kitchen for so long,

128
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,780
but found nothing.

129
00:08:50,820 --> 00:08:52,660
The problem lies in the water.

130
00:08:54,110 --> 00:08:55,570
They boiled these

131
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:58,610
to make tea for you, Your Ladyship.

132
00:09:05,290 --> 00:09:06,150
Your Ladyship.

133
00:09:08,370 --> 00:09:09,230
Your Ladyship.

134
