160
00:10:54,890 --> 00:10:55,750
Your Ladyship.

161
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,590
Lady?

162
00:11:10,210 --> 00:11:11,010
That's right.

163
00:11:12,950 --> 00:11:13,960
At first,

164
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:18,130
I wanted to be a good wife.

165
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:23,700
I just wanted to help him take care of everything outside.

166
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:28,980
He didn't want me to go out all the time.

167
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,710
I obeyed him.

168
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:35,670
I've been guarding this mansion.

169
00:11:37,470 --> 00:11:39,410
He wanted to get concubines.

170
00:11:40,150 --> 00:11:41,650
I just tolerated it.

171
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:44,950
That was because I really loved him.

172
00:11:44,970 --> 00:11:46,900
I really loved him.

173
00:11:47,670 --> 00:11:50,690
I loved him so much that I almost lost myself.

174
00:11:52,070 --> 00:11:53,670
I lived only for this family,

175
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:56,350
for whatever in this family...

176
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:02,710
I even believed

177
00:12:05,460 --> 00:12:08,990
it was my fault for not being able to give birth to a child for him.

178
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:11,710
It turns out

179
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,780
that the problem's not with me.

180
00:12:29,410 --> 00:12:31,010
Your Ladyship, you can't...

181
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,300
Your Ladyship.

