188
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:27,380
Here.

189
00:13:27,900 --> 00:13:29,360
You said you didn't care about Hao Jia.

190
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:31,040
But hearing that she's even in a worse condition after giving birth,

191
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:32,640
you're more worried than anyone else.

192
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:33,080
Stop!

193
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,640
What are you doing?

194
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,640
You don't know me?

195
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:37,490
How dare you stop me and my wife?

196
00:13:37,490 --> 00:13:38,150
Step aside.

197
00:13:39,280 --> 00:13:39,760
Don't.

198
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:40,680
Don't draw your sword.

199
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:41,510
No, you can't do this.

200
00:13:41,510 --> 00:13:42,570
Put the sword away.

201
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:44,580
Sorry.

202
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:45,400
Prince Qi.

203
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:46,000
Lady Jing.

204
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:47,960
What's wrong?

205
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:51,440
Prince Song doesn't allow anyone to visit Concubine Jia.

206
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,880
But Lady Fangru knew it was you,

207
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:54,360
so she asked me to come out and tell you.

208
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,350
Why?

209
00:13:55,760 --> 00:13:57,560
She just gave birth to his child.

210
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,040
What's his problem?

211
00:13:58,040 --> 00:13:58,480
Calm down.

212
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,680
Let's get down to business.

213
00:13:59,680 --> 00:14:00,280
May I ask

214
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:02,100
how Hao Jia's condition is now?

215
00:14:02,700 --> 00:14:04,430
Concubine Jia is grounded.

216
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:07,600
She at first cried day and night,

217
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,600
and was even afraid to see her child.

218
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:10,800
Actually, I've seen such conditions before

219
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:12,270
in the countryside.

220
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:13,880
The women who get possessed

221
00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:15,450
should have loved their babies very much.

222
00:14:15,450 --> 00:14:17,000
But after giving birth,

223
00:14:17,130 --> 00:14:18,160
some may try to kill their babies

224
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:19,490
or even commit suicide.

225
00:14:20,260 --> 00:14:22,090
Her Ladyship also wanted to invite someone to take a look.

226
00:14:22,090 --> 00:14:23,620
But Prince Song forbade it.

227
00:14:25,800 --> 00:14:26,570
What?

228
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:14,170
Concubine Wei wants to see you, Madam.

229
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:20,870
Madam He,

230
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:24,620
the Legitimate Eldest Prince locked up his concubine Hao Jia.

231
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:26,670
I didn't dare to see Madam Xinchuan,

232
00:15:27,830 --> 00:15:29,890
so I came to ask for your help instead.

233
00:15:33,140 --> 00:15:35,460
I'm not the Legitimate Eldest Prince's birth mother.

234
00:15:35,460 --> 00:15:36,440
So I have no right

235
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,240
to interfere in his family issues.

236
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:39,040
I understand.

237
00:15:39,630 --> 00:15:40,960
I overstepped the line.

238
00:15:41,710 --> 00:15:44,420
But I don't know

239
00:15:45,290 --> 00:15:47,630
who else can help me.

240
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:51,470
The Legitimate Eldest Prince is mistreating her.

241
00:15:51,470 --> 00:15:53,000
Her life was already tough.

242
00:15:54,090 --> 00:15:55,620
When she planned to escape,

243
00:15:56,660 --> 00:15:58,260
she found herself pregnant.

244
00:15:59,770 --> 00:16:02,970
The Legitimate Eldest Prince has long been wanting a son.

245
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:05,360
But she gave birth to a daughter

246
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:09,920
and has been suffering postpartum depression.

247
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:11,630
If this goes on, I'm afraid...

248
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,450
You seem to care a lot about her.

249
00:16:15,910 --> 00:16:17,040
My family taught me,

250
00:16:17,690 --> 00:16:18,750
one should neither

251
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:21,930
flatter when your friends are at the pinnacle of life,

252
00:16:21,930 --> 00:16:24,460
nor ignore when your friends fall in trouble.

253
00:16:24,610 --> 00:16:27,090
There's no one backing Hao Jia.

254
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:30,820
If I also do nothing,

255
00:16:31,850 --> 00:16:34,780
she will really be forced into a hopeless situation.

256
00:16:40,470 --> 00:16:41,570
Please, Madam.

257
00:16:50,110 --> 00:16:50,730
Get up.

258
00:16:57,070 --> 00:16:57,970
Just go back.

259
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,060
Madam!

260
00:16:59,170 --> 00:16:59,870
I'm tired.

261
00:17:00,630 --> 00:17:01,430
I want to rest.

262
00:17:29,270 --> 00:17:32,600
Madam, you actually like Sixth Prince's concubine, right?

263
00:17:33,030 --> 00:17:33,740
Maybe.

264
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:38,480
This girl has a sincere heart.

265
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:40,530
Back then,

266
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:43,300
I was not yet 15 when I gave birth to Yin Zheng.

267
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:46,150
If there had been someone like her,

268
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:49,000
I wouldn't have had to...

269
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,480
Are you going to help her?

270
00:17:53,450 --> 00:17:55,980
Actually, it's not difficult to handle this.

271
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:58,340
It's just a matter of begging Lord.

272
00:17:59,040 --> 00:18:01,430
No matter how dissatisfied Madam Xinchuan is,

273
00:18:01,430 --> 00:18:02,780
she'll just mock me.

274
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:04,970
I just thought about how

275
00:18:06,300 --> 00:18:08,760
I was also in depression after giving birth.

276
00:18:09,360 --> 00:18:11,690
I owed my child a lot and lost Lord's favor.

277
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:16,120
The madams who had been close to me never cared about me.

278
00:18:17,230 --> 00:18:18,890
Actually, I don't blame them.

279
00:18:20,420 --> 00:18:22,010
But to live this life,

280
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:24,410
everyone can get into trouble.

281
00:18:25,510 --> 00:18:27,470
Who doesn't want someone to help?

282
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:31,120
If no one

283
00:18:31,120 --> 00:18:33,120
is willing to help for fearing trouble,

284
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:36,310
then what's left between people can only be indifference.

285
00:18:36,310 --> 00:18:37,040
That's true.

286
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:54,120
The imperial physician said

287
00:18:54,120 --> 00:18:55,310
since he couldn't see Hao Jia in person,

288
00:18:55,310 --> 00:19:00,110
he could only prescribe some medicine to help sooth her liver and relieve depression.

289
00:19:02,840 --> 00:19:03,650
What to do...

290
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:09,890
Aren't you going in?

291
00:19:13,600 --> 00:19:16,420
You said you were going to the Imperial Hospital.

292
00:19:17,830 --> 00:19:21,160
It was because you wanted me to see your mother alone, right?

293
00:19:24,470 --> 00:19:27,410
I thought she'd help without me being there.

294
00:19:29,700 --> 00:19:31,100
But now I see, I was wrong.

295
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,960
I'll think of some other ways later.

296
00:19:44,260 --> 00:19:46,390
I heard when my mother gave birth to me,

297
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:47,610
she also cried a lot.

298
00:19:49,540 --> 00:19:51,380
Especially when I was in childhood,

299
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:53,510
I seemed to be like an enemy in her eyes.

300
00:19:54,370 --> 00:19:55,370
I didn't know why.

301
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,970
Maybe it was my problem.

302
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:03,360
Yin Zheng.

303
00:20:04,530 --> 00:20:06,190
Maybe the Madam He at that time

304
00:20:06,890 --> 00:20:09,490
was also sick like Hao Jia.

305
00:20:15,350 --> 00:20:16,010
Believe me.

306
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:18,080
It was not your problem.

307
00:20:20,360 --> 00:20:23,490
After giving birth, women tend to be emotional

308
00:20:24,700 --> 00:20:26,560
and will suffer from depression.

309
00:20:27,430 --> 00:20:29,220
When their condition becomes severe,

310
00:20:29,220 --> 00:20:31,090
they may even feel miserable

311
00:20:32,060 --> 00:20:34,320
when seeing their own babies sometimes.

312
00:20:34,730 --> 00:20:38,440
I'm sure it was not Madam He's real intention to treat you like that.

313
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:39,440
She was just sick.

314
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:42,130
She couldn't control herself.

315
00:20:44,710 --> 00:20:46,110
It was neither her fault,

316
00:20:46,910 --> 00:20:47,880
nor yours.

317
00:20:50,070 --> 00:20:51,270
It was not your fault.

318
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:57,420
Prince Zheng, Concubine Wei.

319
00:20:59,970 --> 00:21:00,980
Madam He has ordered Nanny Wen

320
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:04,040
to go to the Legitimate Eldest Prince's mansion later.

321
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:06,360
Since Nanny Wen can represent Madam He,

322
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:09,450
the Legitimate Eldest Prince will have to let her in.

323
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:18,920
Why did Madam Wen suddenly come

324
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,520
and even brought those guys here?

325
00:21:20,520 --> 00:21:21,440
I don't know.

326
00:21:21,780 --> 00:21:23,710
But Nanny Wen represents Madam He.

327
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:25,180
We can't turn her down.

328
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:33,130
Greetings, Your Highness.

329
00:21:33,910 --> 00:21:35,840
I'm ordered by Madam He to come here

330
00:21:36,040 --> 00:21:37,300
and ask you a question.

331
00:21:37,980 --> 00:21:39,830
Since Concubine Jia gave birth,

332
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:42,170
you've been grounding her in her room.

333
00:21:42,470 --> 00:21:43,600
It's unacceptable.

334
00:21:52,760 --> 00:21:54,140
You have no idea.

335
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:56,720
Since Hao Jia gave birth,

336
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:58,330
she hasn't recovered.

337
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:01,440
So I did this to let her recuperate.

338
00:22:03,130 --> 00:22:03,480
Fine.

339
00:22:04,500 --> 00:22:06,630
But the rumor has spread to the palace.

340
00:22:07,070 --> 00:22:09,870
Please let Hao Jia come out and let me see how she is.

341
00:22:13,890 --> 00:22:14,490
Sure.

342
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:16,520
Bao,

343
00:22:17,730 --> 00:22:19,390
go invite Concubine Jia here.

344
00:22:20,580 --> 00:22:21,510
Let them see her.

345
00:22:21,870 --> 00:22:22,280
Yes.

346
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,090
Hao Jia.

347
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:45,370
Are you okay?

348
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:46,670
How are you?

349
00:22:47,560 --> 00:22:48,240
I'm fine.

350
00:22:48,750 --> 00:22:49,880
Everything is fine.

351
00:22:50,330 --> 00:22:51,280
Don't worry.

352
00:22:58,600 --> 00:22:59,870
If someone threatens you,

353
00:22:59,870 --> 00:23:01,360
you don't have to be afraid.

354
00:23:01,360 --> 00:23:03,900
Or you can come to live in our mansion.

355
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:05,850
What do you mean, Princess?

356
00:23:06,320 --> 00:23:10,110
Hao Jia was selected to my mansion among the girls from the nine regions.

357
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:11,440
Without my permission,

358
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:12,970
she can't leave my mansion.

359
00:23:13,270 --> 00:23:14,730
For what you said just now,

360
00:23:15,520 --> 00:23:18,450
it can be interpreted as you are insulting Xinchuan.

361
00:23:19,880 --> 00:23:20,650
I dare not.

362
00:23:21,080 --> 00:23:22,610
-But Hao Jia... -Princess.

363
00:23:24,180 --> 00:23:25,340
Don't worry.

364
00:23:26,050 --> 00:23:27,110
I'm really fine.

365
00:23:27,950 --> 00:23:29,170
Everything is fine.

366
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:33,770
Henceforth,

367
00:23:35,260 --> 00:23:37,460
be sure to take good care of yourselves.

368
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,480
I don't want to trouble you anymore.

369
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:44,140
And don't come to see me again.

370
00:24:12,830 --> 00:24:14,490
You cooperated well just now.

371
00:24:15,080 --> 00:24:16,290
You being obedient

372
00:24:17,350 --> 00:24:18,590
is really likeable.

373
00:24:21,710 --> 00:24:23,570
You've suffered a lot these days.

374
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:24,930
Take a good rest.

375
00:24:27,930 --> 00:24:29,130
I'll visit you again.

376
00:24:29,600 --> 00:24:31,200
You don't have to come again.

377
00:24:33,040 --> 00:24:36,200
Just go back to your work.

378
00:24:40,600 --> 00:24:41,530
What do you mean?

379
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:42,760
Nothing.

380
00:24:45,110 --> 00:24:45,920
It's just that

381
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,520
I no longer want to

382
00:24:48,520 --> 00:24:50,790
fawn on someone who makes me sick.

383
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,360
You grounded me,

384
00:24:56,020 --> 00:24:56,610
beat me,

385
00:24:57,670 --> 00:24:58,530
humiliated me,

386
00:24:59,790 --> 00:25:01,850
and sought the sense of control on me.

387
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:06,420
It's all because you're powerless in the court, isn't it?

388
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:10,470
You rely on your father's temporary love,

389
00:25:11,380 --> 00:25:14,230
on your legitimate wife's noble family background,

390
00:25:14,230 --> 00:25:16,230
and pin your hope on your unborn son!

391
00:25:17,240 --> 00:25:18,570
You just look powerful.

392
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:20,380
But actually you're nothing.

393
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:23,480
Do you really think you can keep your position

394
00:25:23,620 --> 00:25:27,420
by giving birth to the legitimate eldest grandson of Lord Xinchuan?

395
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:30,960
Everything you have

396
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,160
was all

397
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,190
rewarded by me.

398
00:25:33,490 --> 00:25:35,550
Your family in Yanchuan has nothing.

399
00:25:35,550 --> 00:25:36,350
Without me,

400
00:25:38,110 --> 00:25:40,440
you could even live a worse life than a rat.

401
00:25:41,040 --> 00:25:41,700
Let go of me!

402
00:25:47,170 --> 00:25:49,360
Are you angry after hearing the truth?

403
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:53,090
I like to see you being angry.

404
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:56,020
Do you know why I liked you?

405
00:25:57,310 --> 00:25:59,160
Because you are not like Zhao Fangru.

406
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:00,060
You have nothing.

407
00:26:00,060 --> 00:26:01,660
You can only live at my mercy.

408
00:26:03,660 --> 00:26:04,320
You can only

409
00:26:05,500 --> 00:26:08,560
stay in this yard for the rest of your life,

410
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:11,870
and live on my occasional sympathy.

411
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:15,350
You know it.

412
00:26:16,560 --> 00:26:17,660
Even I

413
00:26:17,760 --> 00:26:20,360
have to live at Lord's mercy.

414
00:26:21,740 --> 00:26:23,730
Even I have to live with a chain on,

415
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:27,480
let alone you.

416
00:26:28,940 --> 00:26:33,890
You're just nobody, inferior to dirt,

417
00:26:35,420 --> 00:26:36,570
having no right

418
00:26:38,420 --> 00:26:40,460
to get respect and dignity.

419
00:26:56,360 --> 00:26:57,890
I will come to see you again.

420
00:26:59,810 --> 00:27:00,610
But remember,

421
00:27:02,410 --> 00:27:04,010
next time when I see you,

422
00:27:05,910 --> 00:27:07,970
you should show me a better attitude.

423
00:27:19,470 --> 00:27:20,130
My Lady!

424
00:27:20,650 --> 00:27:21,900
Are you fine?

425
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:25,550
Nothing.

426
00:27:31,490 --> 00:27:35,250
Send the baby to Lady Fangru.

427
00:27:37,070 --> 00:27:37,890
Tell her,

428
00:27:39,250 --> 00:27:40,850
please take care of the baby.

429
00:27:43,320 --> 00:27:43,920
I'm tired.

430
00:27:46,080 --> 00:27:46,930
I want to rest.

431
00:27:48,280 --> 00:27:49,680
You don't have to come in.

432
00:28:33,880 --> 00:28:35,710
I'm fine now.

433
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,440
Don't worry.

434
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:42,920
Take good care of yourselves.

435
00:28:44,530 --> 00:28:46,530
I don't want to trouble you anymore.

436
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:48,380
And don't come to see me again.

437
00:28:50,650 --> 00:28:52,560
Could it be that only if I die

438
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:55,050
can this be ended?

439
00:29:04,490 --> 00:29:05,260
What's wrong?

440
00:29:05,260 --> 00:29:06,000
Your Ladyship.

441
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:08,080
I don't know why the horse stopped.

442
00:29:25,390 --> 00:29:26,520
I have a bad feeling.

443
00:29:27,280 --> 00:29:27,880
Yuan Ying.

444
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:29,360
Something is wrong with Hao Jia.

445
00:29:29,360 --> 00:29:29,680
No.

446
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:31,360
Something is very wrong.

447
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:32,330
I need to go back.

448
00:29:32,360 --> 00:29:33,220
Please go find Yin Zheng.

449
00:29:33,220 --> 00:29:33,550
Okay.

450
00:29:43,260 --> 00:29:46,360
♫Longing for softness♫

451
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:49,880
♫Harvesting what was planted♫

452
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:54,180
♫Gaining a moment of pleasure♫

453
00:29:54,610 --> 00:29:57,830
♫Bearing endless sorrow♫

454
00:29:58,890 --> 00:30:01,940
♫Writing down a dirge♫

455
00:30:02,550 --> 00:30:06,030
♫Falling behind the flying time♫

456
00:30:04,020 --> 00:30:07,170
[Last words of Hao Jia]

457
00:30:06,510 --> 00:30:13,500
♫Life is still long, how will it drag by?♫

458
00:30:14,610 --> 00:30:15,840
♫Like the autumn scenery♫

459
00:30:16,470 --> 00:30:17,640
♫Like blooming fireworks♫

460
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:21,500
♫Gone in a twinkling♫

461
00:30:22,290 --> 00:30:23,620
♫With only silence left♫

462
00:30:24,190 --> 00:30:25,410
♫But I'm still obsessed♫

463
00:30:26,050 --> 00:30:32,200
♫With being a moth, flying to the flames♫

464
00:30:33,490 --> 00:30:41,200
♫Singly stepping on the one-log bridge regardless of the strong wind, going astray♫

465
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:36,240
Since I'm here to get selected to the palace,

466
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:38,960
I shall choose Xinchuan, for it's the best among the nine regions.

467
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,220
Since I'm in Xinchuan,

468
00:30:40,360 --> 00:30:42,530
I want to be selected by a master with the best prospects.

469
00:30:41,620 --> 00:30:48,800
♫No looking back while the way ahead has no end♫

470
00:30:42,850 --> 00:30:45,710
Shouldn't the one be the Legitimate Eldest Prince?

471
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:56,890
♫Just make myself trapped by obsession, and keep falling♫

472
00:30:50,030 --> 00:30:50,870
You can only

473
00:30:51,710 --> 00:30:54,040
stay in this yard for the rest of your life,

474
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:58,440
and live on my occasional sympathy.

475
00:30:57,560 --> 00:31:03,130
♫No one knows, I used♫

476
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:08,400
♫To drift with wind♫

477
00:31:09,080 --> 00:31:12,430
♫And learned how hard it is to know one's true heart♫

478
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:14,000
How can I not wish you well?

479
00:31:12,950 --> 00:31:20,060
♫How should I go through the abyss-like palace life?♫

480
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:16,310
But after you leave,

481
00:31:16,520 --> 00:31:18,450
if the Second Prince ask me for you,

482
00:31:18,520 --> 00:31:20,600
what should your father and I do?

483
00:31:21,030 --> 00:31:22,390
♫Sighing for the blossom fall♫

484
00:31:21,430 --> 00:31:23,150
If the prince of Xinchuan gets furious,

485
00:31:22,970 --> 00:31:24,160
♫Sighing for the sunset♫

486
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:25,170
Lord Yanchuan will punish your father.

487
00:31:24,740 --> 00:31:28,130
♫For the bit of desolation♫

488
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:29,410
Then it's over for my family.

489
00:31:28,790 --> 00:31:30,030
♫It looks delicate♫

490
00:31:30,820 --> 00:31:32,180
♫It looks lonely♫

491
00:31:32,490 --> 00:31:38,690
♫Knowing the destiny but still choosing to accept it♫

492
00:31:32,560 --> 00:31:33,590
I hope

493
00:31:33,750 --> 00:31:34,870
in the future,

494
00:31:35,150 --> 00:31:37,730
I can see my husband's smile every day.

495
00:31:40,250 --> 00:31:47,690
♫Singly stepping on the one-log bridge regardless of the strong wind, going astray♫

496
00:31:46,630 --> 00:31:47,360
Hao Jia.

497
00:31:47,850 --> 00:31:48,730
Please wait for me.

498
00:31:48,140 --> 00:31:51,850
♫No looking back while the way ahead has no end♫

499
00:31:51,840 --> 00:31:54,350
Life in the backyard should be in peace and harmony.

500
00:31:52,030 --> 00:31:55,540
♫What's right and what's wrong?♫

501
00:31:54,730 --> 00:31:56,540
When we grow old,

502
00:31:56,060 --> 00:31:59,590
♫It has already been decided by the fate♫

503
00:31:56,840 --> 00:31:59,960
we can go to the backyard to bask in the sunshine.

504
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:03,540
♫Love, hatred, separation and reunion♫

505
00:32:04,070 --> 00:32:07,390
♫To look back, the one is still the same♫

506
00:32:07,830 --> 00:32:10,100
♫Clouds drift by along with the wind♫

507
00:32:38,840 --> 00:32:39,700
Stop! You're not allowed in!

508
00:32:39,700 --> 00:32:40,420
Let me in!

509
00:32:40,530 --> 00:32:41,650
Let me see Hao Jia.

510
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,520
Concubine Jia is resting.

511
00:32:42,520 --> 00:32:43,660
Let me in.

512
00:32:43,840 --> 00:32:44,290
No.

513
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:46,970
Put down the sword.

514
00:32:46,970 --> 00:32:47,440
Step aside!

515
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:48,470
Help!

516
00:32:48,650 --> 00:32:50,580
Concubine Jia committed suicide.

517
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:56,570
Hao Jia!

518
00:32:58,480 --> 00:32:58,940
This...

519
00:33:20,310 --> 00:33:21,510
Prepare the funeral.

520
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:24,050
What funeral?

521
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:27,050
Why?

522
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:29,910
You can't just take a glance

523
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,950
and ask us to prepare the funeral.

524
00:33:31,950 --> 00:33:34,680
You can treat her with acupuncture or medicine, anything is fine.

525
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,130
No.

526
00:33:35,570 --> 00:33:36,370
No.

527
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:37,840
We can't prepare the funeral.

528
00:33:37,840 --> 00:33:38,900
I've tried my best.

529
00:33:39,360 --> 00:33:40,600
Concubine Jia has been in the water for too long.

530
00:33:40,600 --> 00:33:42,000
There's almost no pulse.

531
00:33:42,360 --> 00:33:43,600
I'm afraid there's no hope.

532
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:44,660
Please take a look.

533
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:46,040
Please have a look!

534
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:47,170
Please take a look!

535
00:33:48,120 --> 00:33:50,200
If it doesn't work, we can get more imperial physicians.

536
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:52,170
We can get many imperial physicians.

537
00:33:52,170 --> 00:33:53,450
Please save her.

538
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:54,080
Your Ladyship!

539
00:33:54,080 --> 00:33:55,160
Please get up.

540
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,840
Let me think.

541
00:33:56,840 --> 00:33:58,450
Let me think.

542
00:34:01,520 --> 00:34:02,320
Physician Xu.

543
00:34:02,760 --> 00:34:04,190
Physician Xu may have a way.

544
00:34:04,190 --> 00:34:06,360
He once rescued a person who has been in suffocation for a long time.

545
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:07,750
But his identity is special.

546
00:34:07,750 --> 00:34:09,949
I'm afraid it's hard to invite him here.

547
00:34:10,070 --> 00:34:11,350
Physician Xu.

548
00:34:12,250 --> 00:34:13,110
Damn, bad luck!

549
00:34:13,230 --> 00:34:14,920
How dare she do this after giving birth?

550
00:34:14,920 --> 00:34:16,110
This is humiliating!

551
00:34:16,110 --> 00:34:17,219
Why didn't she die outside?

552
00:34:17,219 --> 00:34:18,080
Your Highness.

553
00:34:18,290 --> 00:34:19,690
Please watch your mouth.

554
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:20,800
Li Wei!

555
00:34:21,080 --> 00:34:21,610
How is it?

556
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,130
Prince Song,

557
00:34:23,199 --> 00:34:24,360
I beg for your mercy

558
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:25,909
Please go to the palace and invite Physician Xu

559
00:34:25,909 --> 00:34:26,670
to save Hao Jia.

560
00:34:26,670 --> 00:34:27,630
Physician Xu?

